# рҹҺ“ Sanmati Engineering College вҖ” WhatsApp Admission Bot
## Full System Report

---

## 1. System Overview

This is a **production-ready WhatsApp Admission Automation System** built for Sanmati Engineering College. It provides two main capabilities:

1. **AI Admission Counselor** вҖ” An intelligent WhatsApp chatbot that answers student queries about admissions, fees, placements, hostel, etc., using an AI model powered by OpenRouter.
2. **Marketing Broadcast Tool** вҖ” A standalone script to send bulk WhatsApp template messages to CET students from a CSV/Excel file.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["рҹ“ұ Student sends<br>WhatsApp message"] --> B["вҳҒпёҸ Meta Cloud API"]
    B -->|Webhook POST| C["рҹҢҚ ngrok tunnel"]
    C --> D["вҡЎ FastAPI Server<br>(uvicorn on port 8000)"]
    D --> E{"Message Router"}
    E -->|"1, 2, or 3"| F["рҹ“Ӣ Menu Templates<br>(Engineering/ITI/Nursing)"]
    E -->|"hi, hello, menu"| G["рҹҷҸ Welcome Message"]
    E -->|"Free-text question"| H["рҹӨ– OpenRouter AI<br>(stepfun/step-3.5-flash)"]
    F --> I["рҹ“Ө WhatsApp API<br>Send Response"]
    G --> I
    H --> I
    I --> J["рҹ“ұ Student receives reply"]
    D --> K["рҹ—„пёҸ SQLite Database<br>(sanmati.db)"]
    K --> L["рҹ‘Ө Students Table"]
    K --> M["рҹ’¬ Interactions Table"]
    D --> N["рҹ”Ҙ Hot Lead Detection"]
```

---

## 2. Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| **Framework** | FastAPI (Python) | Async web server for webhook handling |
| **Server** | Uvicorn | ASGI server with hot-reload |
| **Database** | SQLAlchemy + SQLite | Student records & interaction logging |
| **AI Brain** | OpenRouter API (`stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free`) | Knowledge-based admission counselor |
| **WhatsApp** | Meta WhatsApp Cloud API (direct `httpx` calls) | Send/receive messages |
| **Tunnel** | ngrok | Expose local server to the internet |
| **Broadcast** | pandas + httpx | Bulk marketing message sender |

