## 7. How to Start the System

```bash
# 1. Start the FastAPI server
python -m uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000

# 2. Start ngrok tunnel (in a separate terminal)
ngrok http 8000

# 3. Configure webhook in Meta Developer Portal:
#    Callback URL: https://<ngrok-url>/webhook
#    Verify Token: sanmati_webhook_secret_2025
#    Subscribe to: messages
```

